Map: Fy_Kyanite
Type: Fun Yard
Version: BETA
Description: Fy_Kyanite is the sort of map which requires speed and HEADSHOTS!
The Closer you get to the enemy the more dangerous.. BUT the better your gun.
Stay alive? And keep your gun for the next round.
Use the Cars & Trucks for Cover.. they're there for a reason!
This is only a BETA Version. I know i messed something up in Hammer to make the floor tilted and weird Anyways. Please Wait for Fy_Kyanite2 and hopefully it will be fixed.

www.hellclan.co.uk
